# Licorn Project

## Documentation

Please visit http://docs.licorn.org/ for up-to-date content. In fact the website
is an HTML version of the `docs/` directory (generated via `Sphinx`).

## Project / Editor / Conventions / Notes

### GEANY

*.py;*.rst;*.md;Makefile;README*;*.txt;*.html;*.csv;*.conf;*.css;*.ldif;*.js

### Debugging the daemon / start-stop process

	while true; do clear; ps ax | grep licorn | grep -vE '(grep|tail)'; sleep 2; done

